It could a combination of **[Frutiger Pro (65 Bold)](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317113325/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Linotype%20%2F%20%28Commercial%29&ffam=Frutiger%20LT%20Pro%20-%2065%20Bold&fid=7c3e5db8678256ec3d993956f9435a60&fsize=60&text=Jesmond&wrap=2)**  
and **[Frutiger Next (Light)](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317113325/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Linotype%20%2F%20%28Commercial%29&ffam=Frutiger%20Next%20Com%20-%20Light&fid=17e7ac1cecb107b1c7a296f31c00850c&fsize=60&text=Therapy%20Centre&fit=1)**
Looks about right to me. Thank you so much for the help.
